data.description: 5 Bedroom 2 Bath home in the Penn Harris Madison School Corporation with just less than one acre of land. The public records do not include the 576 square footage of the attached garage converted into 2-Bedrooms and 1-full bath for total square footage of 2572.  The property includes walk-up stairs to the attic for an additional 1200 square feet, which could be finished to a new owner's liking.  There is a large Pole Barn/3-Car Garage that easily fits 3-cars.  The property is grandfathered in to having a well and septic, but city water and sewer are available currently right at the street.  A few updates include a new well tank and pump 2021.  New AC 2017.  Electric panel is 110v but there is a 220v line already ran to the garage.   The Property is Being Sold "As-Is"
